body:
45.5K lines TS/TSX + 22K CSS measured on 1301404d. Rounds: A dead code +
dep hygiene + knip-in-CI; B app-shell decomposition (31 useState/36 fns,
five blade lines to finish the half-done extraction, target <900 lines);
C CSS strata consolidation (tokens 1509 lines + parallel token systems);
D duplicate helpers (measured small — formatBytes ×3, mountedRef ×6).
knip false-positives documented (storybook globs, ui dist tests).

- remove the decorative 技能示例 section (SKILL_EXAMPLE_CARDS + dead CSS);
  the 添加 CTA already seeds a real, editable starter skill
- make createStarterSkill idempotent: a repeat 添加 reuses the existing
  starter-skill (created:false) instead of minting duplicate 示例技能 rows;
  renderer toasts 「已打开现有示例技能」 on reuse
- add deleteSkill (path-hardened rm) with skills:delete IPC + preload bridge
  and a per-row 删除 action using a two-step 确认删除 in-place confirm;
  refreshes the 内置 catalog so a deleted bundled skill reappears installable
- re-pin skills.test.ts contracts: example-card/section pins → absence pins,
  second-create → reuse invariant; add delete + idempotent coverage
